    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel the <strong> courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of courgette ribbons</p><p>Dice the <strong>inner</strong> <strong>stem<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-lean-pork-with-sultanas-and-courgette-couscous/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong> and <strong>sultanas</strong> to a large dish or bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover and set aside</p><p>Add the<strong> courgette ribbons</strong> to a pot or separate heat-proof bowl and cover with hot water for 4 min, then drain and squeeze out any excess water with your hands</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-lean-pork-with-sultanas-and-courgette-couscous/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-lean-pork-with-sultanas-and-courgette-couscous/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>cumin seeds</strong> and <strong>ground smoked</strong> <strong>paprika</strong> and toast the spices for 30 secs</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and the <strong>diced</strong> <strong>red onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 3 min over a medium heat</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-lean-pork-with-sultanas-and-courgette-couscous/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>mince</strong> to the pan and cook for 5 min, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>diced courgette</strong>, cook for a further 2 min, then add the <strong>chicken stock</strong></p><p>Cook the mince mixture for 5 min further or until the stock has absorbed and the mince mixture is glazed and cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your <strong>smoky mince</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-lean-pork-with-sultanas-and-courgette-couscous/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from the stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Wash the <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-lean-pork-with-sultanas-and-courgette-couscous/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Fluff the <strong>sultanas couscous</strong> with a fork and stir in the <strong>courgette ribbons</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion, chopped mint </strong>and<strong> salad</strong></p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>sultanas & courgette couscous</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-lean-pork-with-sultanas-and-courgette-couscous/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>mince </strong>over the <strong>sultanas & courgette couscous</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
